—significantly increase force levels but not achieve a higher pace of
                    modernization than currently assessed as likely (NIE 11–3/8–75, Force 4 force levels, but Force 2 or lower
                    qualitative improvements);

—maintain roughly present strategic force levels, but modernize them at a pace
                    significantly higher than presently considered likely (NIE 11–3/8–75, Force 2 quantitative levels, but Force 4 qualitative
                    improvements);
